"Additional High Rank Sections":
"New Ranks have been added to High Rank Sections.

Higher level enemies means better rewards, but your Power Level needs to be higher before you can enter."

"In the new High Rank Sections, there is a chance that PSE Bursts will become \"PSE Burst f\" (forte), in which only rare enemies and Megalotix will appear.

PSE Burst Encores may also become PSE Burst f."
"Trials featuring Aina and Manon will always trigger a PSE Burst on completion, regardless of your PSE Level."
